<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ثَوبٍ مِنَ الْجَهْلِ الْمُرَكَّبِ فَوقَهُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ثَوْبُ التّعَصُّبِ بِئْسَتِ الثَّوبَانِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وتَحَلَّ بِالإِنْصَافِ أَفْخَرَ حُلَّةٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>زِينَتْ بِهَا الأَعْطَافُ وَالْكَتِفَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَاجْعَل شِعَارَكَ خَشْيَةَ الرَّحْمَنِ مَعْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>نُصْحِ الرّسُولِ فَحَبَّذَا الأَمْرَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَتَمَسكَنَّ بِحَبْلِهِ وَبِوَحْيِهِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَتَوَكَّلَنَّ حَقِيقَةَ التُّكْلاَنِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَالْحَقُّ وَصْفُ الرّبِّ وَهُوَ صِرَاطُهُ الْـ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>ـهَادِي إِلَيْهِ لِصَاحِبِ الإيمَانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَهُوَ الصِّرَاطُ عَلَيْهِ رَبُّ الْعَرْشِ أَيْـ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>ـضًا وَذَا قَدْ جَاءَ فِي الْقُرْآنِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَالْحَقُّ مَنْصُورٌ وَمُمْتَحَنٌ فَلاَ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>تَعْجَبْ فَهَذِي سُنَّةُ الرَّحْمَنِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَبِذَاكَ يَظْهَرُ حِزْبُهُ مِنْ حَرْبِهِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَلأَجْلِ ذَاكَ النَّاسُ طَائِفَتَانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَلأَجْلِ ذَاكَ الْحَرْبُ بَيْنَ الرُّسِلِ وَالْـ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>ـكُفَّارِ مُذْ قَامَ الْوَرَى سِجْلاَنِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>لَكِنَّمَا الْعُقبَى لأَهْلِ الْحَقِّ إِنْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَاتَتْ هُنَا كَانَتْ لَدَى الدَّيَّانِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَاجْعَلْ لِقَلْبِكَ هِجْرَتَيْنِ وَلاَ تَنَمْ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>